Sample SpaCy NER code:
```
import spacy

nlp = spacy.load("en_core_web_sm")
docs = [
  nlp(u"Apple is looking at buying U.K. startup for $1 billion"),
  nlp(u"Ron Swanson"),
  nlp(u"Bab Ross Inc."),
  nlp(u"Ronnie Contractor Inc."),
  nlp(u"91 Park Street")
]

for doc in docs:
  for ent in doc.ents:
      print(ent.text, ent.start_char, ent.end_char, ent.label_)
  print('\n\n')
```
